{
  "stem": "8610.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you know the entry to Palestine is only by certificates issued by the mandatory authorities.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there aren't any available.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I said to him, you know, if I were to go back to Belsen, say to these young people, 'You're stuck; Palestine is closed for you,' I don't guarantee they won't hang themselves from the rafters of the huts.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He said, I'm terribly sorry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I left empty-handed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was in London.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I thought I must go and see one person in particular.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went to see Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Weizmann, who was the, spokesman of Anglo Jewry as far as the world was concerned, highly respected, we thought, by the government, the leader of the Zionist movement.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I went to see him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was an old, sick man at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I went to him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I told him the situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He listened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He's going grayer and grayer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He said to me, my boy, there was a time when I entered the colonial office through the front door.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now I go through the back door like a schnorrer, like a beggar.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Well, I don't know whether I controlled myself enough, but I felt as though I was drowning myself in tears.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The great fightsman, the man who the world looked to as the leader of the Zionist movement, he, too, was helpless.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "His hands were tied.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Well, I went back to Belsen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I didn't dare tell them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But one thing I did know, that they were determined to get there whatever happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
